# Ternary Bitwise Logic Immediate

TLI-Form

* ternlogi RT, RA, RB, TLI (Rc=0)
* ternlogi. RT, RA, RB, TLI (Rc=1)

Pseudo-code:

    result <- [0] * XLEN
    idx <- [0] * 3
    do i = 0 to XLEN - 1
      idx[0] <- (RT)[i]
      idx[1] <- (RA)[i]
      idx[2] <- (RB)[i]
      result[i] <- (TLI & ROTL64(1, idx)) != 0
    RT <- result

Special Registers Altered:

    CR0                    (if Rc=1)
